&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The big picture:&lt;/strong&gt; Axios is a media company dedicated to providing trustworthy, award-winning news content in an audience-first format. We are hiring an Associate Director, Client Partnerships to join our growing advertising team, reporting to the Head of Strategic Partnerships!&lt;/p&gt;
