&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Go deeper: &lt;/strong&gt;Ideal candidates will embody an entrepreneurial spirit and passion for Axios’ mission. This is a high-energy role with a hunting mentality that requires superior communication skills, ruthless prioritization, an ability to understand partner business priorities and develop creative solutions, and a proven ability to generate leads.&lt;/p&gt;
