&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;5+ years’ experience in sales, specifically in the digital media/news industry&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Established relationships with key agencies and brands&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience in an outbound sales environment&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Understanding of digital media, online marketing technology, and Axios’ competitive landscape&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Exceptionally collaborative, both within your own team and cross-functionally&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Willingness to travel and attend social events and engagements&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Growth mindset with hunger to constantly learn and improve your craft&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
