&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The big picture:&lt;/strong&gt; Axios is a modern media company dedicated to providing trustworthy, award-winning news content in an audience-first format. We are hiring a Local Branded Content Writer to join our brand studio team!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Why it matters:&lt;/strong&gt; The Local Branded Content Writer will develop branded content for Axios’ local advertising partners. As a member of the Branded Content team, you will work with the Branded Content Editor and local revenue partners to build and maintain thought leadership, community-based, and brand marketing campaigns in our trademark Smart Brevity style.&lt;/p&gt;
