&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The big picture:&lt;/strong&gt; Axios is a media company dedicated to providing trustworthy, award-winning news content in an audience-first format. We&#39;re hiring a Managing Director of Expansion &amp;amp; Growth for Axios Local Client Partnerships, who will report to the Head of Sales, Local.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Why it matters:&lt;/strong&gt; The Managing Director of Expansion &amp;amp; Growth will lead a high-velocity, audience-based sales team responsible for driving multi-market, regional revenue growth across the markets that Axios serves.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The details&lt;/strong&gt;: This leader will build a disciplined, package-first sales culture that drives multi-product adoption, increases ACV, and sales velocity.&amp;nbsp; As a builder and performance driver, you will develop hunters who sell audience solutions at scale.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Worthy of your time:&lt;/strong&gt; This is a high-energy role that requires superior communication skills, an ability to understand partner business priorities and develop creative solutions, and a proven ability to generate leads. Ideal candidates will also have the following skills:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;10+ years’ experience in sales, specifically in the digital media industry&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience leading distributed, high-velocity sales teams at scale&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Has multi-market sales experience and knows how regional budgets differ from single-market budgets&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience in consultative selling and can reframe clients around funnel gaps.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;In-depth knowledge of digital media, online marketing technology, and Axios’ competitive landscape&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong CRM discipline and forecasting rigor&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Suggest AI workflows to improve revenue generation and Client Partner effectiveness&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Willingness to travel and attend social events and engagements during evening hours&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to oversee all aspects of daily operations for a team of client partners, including hiring, training, coaching and development, and performance management.&lt;/li&gt;
