&lt;li&gt;Comfort writing in a conversational, reader-first voice&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Equally comfortable doing original reporting and smart aggregation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with newsletters or audience-focused writing&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Familiarity with our Smart Brevity style (or willingness to learn fast)&lt;/li&gt;
