&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The big picture:&lt;/strong&gt; Axios is a media company dedicated to providing trustworthy, award-winning news content in an audience-first format. We are hiring a reporter to be our subject matter expert on the Future of Defense in space.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Why it matters: &lt;/strong&gt;This reporter will enhance our coverage of defense by becoming &lt;em&gt;the&lt;/em&gt; authority on the big topics and trends that are profoundly shaping militaries, geopolitics, and warfare &lt;em&gt;above&lt;/em&gt; the globe now and in the future. These topics include the rising importance of launch capacity, protecting and attacking satellite infrastructure and cutting-edge technologies pushing warfare and national security into orbit.&lt;/p&gt;
